<br>
&quot;Yes, Master, I understand&quot; was all she could say..<br>
<br>
how could the one she loved have changed to much in so short a time, she asked herself.  <br>
<br>
&quot;No, I know he is in there&quot; she thought to herself.  And she resolved herself to endure whatever hardship, whatever fear, whatever pain that would come to save and regain her dearest love...her Hakkin.<br>
